data.meta_description: Tragedy Trail — McCulley, Johnston — Tragedy Trail - Johnston McCulley - Tragedy Trail was written in the year 1919 by Johnston McCulley. This book is one of the most popular novels of Johnston McCulley, and has been translated into several other languages around the world.
